<plot>Never before, has there been a tool like this available to aspiring artists, singer's, song writer's, musicians, and all others seeking to gain stardom within the music industry. This informative 90 minute DVD takes you behind the doors and into the minds of major label A&amp;R's, record company CEO's, entertainment attorneys, sound engineers, managers, promoters, distributors, celebrities, and famous producers whom have produced artists such as; Michael Jackson, Beyonce', Motley Crue, Lil' Kim, Puff Daddy, Notorious B.I.G., Will Smith, Angie Stone, and Madonna, just to name a few. This brilliantly created film is the bridge over various pitfall's that most artists face daily. Learn how to turn yourself into a million dollar asset from industry executives of labels such as: Arista Records, Bad Boys Entertainment, TVT Records, Mia Mind Music, Def Jam and many others. From this informative tool you will gain invaluable information, trade secrets, and step by step guidance for any individual to reach stardom.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?248655</url></doc>
